  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"3.3.2\" data-text=\"Version 3.3.2\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 3.3.2</h3>\n<p>August 7, 2024</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.paging:paging-*:3.3.2</code> is released. Version 3.3.2 contains <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/358f66daa422fdd114efe0c11683c70b47ba1051..1c46a8d0eefa9cf9c4b07e28ebd88a0d737a0508/paging\">these commits</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>New Features</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">paging-common</code> and <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">paging-testing</code> has added new Kotlin-Multiplatform targets: <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">watchos</code>, <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">tvos</code>, and  <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">linuxArm64</code>\n(<a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+/90c97683b9811e57c63ddb93d87b6fa21f02bcde\">90c9768</a>),\n(<a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+/53e0eca80fb98486e38db466d6cb2449c7cecd1f\">53e0eca</a>)</li>\n</ul>",
